These are the main features of the project:

1) User can register a new account, and login using that account.
2) User can search for an particular product.
3) User can view additional details of a specific product.
4) User can add/remove items from cart.
5) User can place an order for the items he has in cart.
6) User can generate an invoice for a particular order he/she made.

Future work:
1) Create a Recommender System.
2) Add sorting, and filtering features.
